## File Map (key files only)

```text
backend/
  app/
    main.py          -- FastAPI app, CORS, router registration
    config.py        -- pydantic-settings, reads .env
    db.py            -- engine (NullPool), SessionLocal, get_db()
    models.py        -- Lead SQLAlchemy model, BudgetBucket/SyncStatus enums
    schemas.py       -- Pydantic request/response DTOs, email validation
    broadcast.py     -- In-memory SSE EventBroadcaster
    routes/
      leads.py       -- POST /api/leads, GET /api/leads, GET /api/leads/stream
      analytics.py   -- GET /api/analytics
      hubspot_status.py -- GET /api/hubspot/status
    services/
      hubspot.py     -- sync_contact(), check_connection(), HubSpotSyncError
  tests/             -- conftest.py + test_*.py files

frontend/
  app/page.tsx       -- Main SPA: form + dashboard + SSE subscription
  components/        -- LeadForm, LeadFeed, AnalyticsBadges, HubSpotStatus
  lib/
    config.ts        -- API_BASE_URL, ENDPOINTS, BUDGET_OPTIONS
    schemas.ts       -- Zod schemas mirroring backend DTOs
    api.ts           -- fetch wrappers with Zod parsing
  __tests__/         -- Vitest component and schema tests
```
